  "detailed_description": "<h1>Play Soul Stalker</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bullet Heaven with Paper Mario-Inspired Graphics</h2></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491670/extras/6c1454a96a4a2ab479556959705426b4.poster.avif?t=1756985818\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491670/extras/6c1454a96a4a2ab479556959705426b4.webm?t=1756985818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491670/extras/6c1454a96a4a2ab479556959705426b4.mp4?t=1756985818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Wanted Shadows is <strong>Vampire Survivors X Action Gameplay</strong><br><br>A bullet heaven/horde survival set in a world where monsters fight over territory. Defeat monsters, power up with permanent upgrades, and become an unstoppable force.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491670/extras/73129578433bf8b1109ddb0877f45917.poster.avif?t=1756985818\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491670/extras/73129578433bf8b1109ddb0877f45917.webm?t=1756985818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491670/extras/73129578433bf8b1109ddb0877f45917.mp4?t=1756985818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>SYNERGISE |</strong> Build the ultimate loadout by choosing, merging, and upgrading weapons and trinkets.<br></li><li> <strong>PROGRESS |</strong> Use the money obtained from runs to buy new characters, weapons, and permanent equippable powers.<br></li><li> <strong>MASTER |</strong> Master the combat system that allows you to dodge, attack, and decimate your enemies.<br></li><li> <strong>GRAPHICS |</strong> Savour the Octopath Traveler-inspired graphics that mix 2D and 3D.<br></li><li> <strong>MUSIC |</strong> Bless your eardrums with a soundtrack of beautiful handmade melodic RPG tracks.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491670/extras/21dafe51f2c4771bc10fa48d66ab4151.poster.avif?t=1756985818\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491670/extras/21dafe51f2c4771bc10fa48d66ab4151.webm?t=1756985818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491670/extras/21dafe51f2c4771bc10fa48d66ab4151.mp4?t=1756985818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You'll Like Wanted Shadows if you like</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Vampire Survivors<br></li><li> Brotato<br></li><li> 20 Minutes Till Dawn<br></li><li> Soul Stalker<br></li><li> Spellbook Demonslayers<br></li><li> Bio Prototype<br></li><li> Peglin<br></li><li> Octopath Traveler<br></li><li> Risk of Rain<br></li><li> Bounty of One<br></li><li> Rogue: Genesia</li></ul>",
